{
  "texts": [
    "For two perturbations (LC10ad and LC10bc), the genetic lines silenced two LC neuron types together.",
    "For simplicity, we assigned each of these to its own model LC unit, which represented the summed activity of all neurons from both types (for example, LC10a and LC10d for LC10ad).",
    "Because the LC bottleneck reads from all 10 past time frames, each model LC unit integrates information over time (for example, for motion detection).",
    "Additionally, the model LC responses are guaranteed to be nonnegative because of the relu activation functions.",
    "Decision network."
  ]
}